## Portfolio framing

When you publish this project, lead with these points:

- Natural-language retrieval instead of simple collaborative filtering.
- Modular ML/AI pipeline that can swap between local and API-based semantic search.
- Human-centric filters: mood, audience, rating quality, and reading length.
- Demo interface that makes the recommender easy to understand in under one minute.

## Known limitations

- The default metadata enrichment is keyword-based for speed and offline reproducibility.
- OpenAI and transformer-based enrichment are optional because they depend on external services or large local models.
- This dataset contains sparse or inconsistent category labels, so some topic labels are heuristic.

## Next improvements

1. Add evaluation on held-out title similarity pairs.
2. Deploy the Gradio demo to Hugging Face Spaces.
3. Add user feedback logging for online reranking.
